01:09:03.742 --> 01:09:05.073
-- How do you know? -- Jeremy just told me.
Chris, get me Salt Lake.

01:09:05.143 --> 01:09:06.406
-- Jeremy.
-- They use dogs.

01:09:06.478 --> 01:09:08.310
Do you know
what a bomb looks like?

01:09:08.380 --> 01:09:09.541
