shepherd can pick one out.

01:09:15.185 --> 01:09:16.551
-- They smell them.
-- They smell them?

01:09:16.621 --> 01:09:18.020
-- <i>Yes. Chris?
Chris: Salt Lake's up.</i>

01:09:18.089 --> 01:09:19.352
-- They're trained in this?
-- Yes. Dave?

01:09:19.424 --> 01:09:20.823
