01:09:20.892 --> 01:09:22.121
-- Well-trained?
-- What?

01:09:22.193 --> 01:09:23.752
-- Their sense of smell
-- it's superior? -- Yes.

01:09:23.828 --> 01:09:26.593
Let's see one through five, and
I need Cincinnati. Dan, Casey --

