stay in this building right now?

01:09:43.314 --> 01:09:45.180
<i>In 10 minutes, 3 1/2 million
people will tune in</i>

01:09:45.250 --> 01:09:47.309
<i>to watch the two of you
on television.</i>

01:09:47.385 --> 01:09:49.046
