01:09:51.622 --> 01:09:53.352
-- All right.
-- Okay.

01:09:54.959 --> 01:09:56.859
10 minutes live.

01:10:12.010 --> 01:10:13.671
Alan, thanks for holding.

01:10:13.745 --> 01:10:16.680
I'm in Isaac's office.
I know I saw it on his desk.

01:10:16.748 --> 01:10:17.840
[Knock on door]

01:10:17.916 --> 01:10:20.351
It's gonna be
in, uh, outline form,

01:10:20.418 --> 01:10:23.046
