01:10:23.121 --> 01:10:24.316
The deficit overlay?

01:10:24.389 --> 01:10:26.483
That sounds fine.

01:10:26.558 --> 01:10:28.356
We can meet at 4:00
if you like.

01:10:28.426 --> 01:10:29.621
No, wait, I'm sorry.

01:10:29.694 --> 01:10:31.287
I've got a rundown at 4:00.

01:10:31.362 --> 01:10:32.887
We can meet at 6:30.

01:10:32.964 --> 01:10:34.762
Good. Thanks.

01:10:34.833 --> 01:10:36.597
I spoke to him
just this morning.

01:10:36.668 --> 01:10:38.158
He sounds awfully good.

01:10:38.236 --> 01:10:41.467
Yes, I spoke to him
just this morning.

01:10:41.539 --> 01:10:43.906
I will. [ Laughs]
Thanks.

01:10:43.975 --> 01:10:45.443
You spoke to Isaac
this morning?

01:10:45.510 --> 01:10:47.672
No, I spoke to Esther.
Isaac couldn't --

01:10:47.746 --> 01:10:50.340
