of this?</i>

01:10:52.150 --> 01:10:53.345
Sign of what?

01:10:53.418 --> 01:10:55.409
Of Isaac having a stroke --
was there any sign of this?

01:10:55.487 --> 01:10:57.581
-- VVas there any sign of Isaac
having a stroke... -- Yes.

01:10:57.655 --> 01:10:59.282
Other than Isaac
having a stroke?

01:10:59.357 --> 01:11:02.019
Dana, it's unbecoming of you to
blame me for any part of this.

01:11:02.093 --> 01:11:04.892
It's a shame, J.J., 'cause I want
so much to be attractive to you.

01:11:04.963 --> 01:11:07.091
You know, we're going to
have to work together.

01:11:07.165 --> 01:11:08.189
Yes, I know.

01:11:08.266 --> 01:11:10.598
For instance, I can help you
with the deficit overlay.

01:11:10.668 --> 01:11:12.636
Isaac kept me up to speed.

01:11:12.704 --> 01:11:14.638
