that Isaac's healthier than he is --

01:11:14.706 --> 01:11:16.470
for instance, if you want
to create the impression

01:11:16.541 --> 01:11:18.305
that Isaac's still
in control of the show

01:11:18.376 --> 01:11:20.208
when olearly he's unable to
even speak on the telephone --

01:11:20.278 --> 01:11:21.712
I can help you there, too.

01:11:21.780 --> 01:11:24.249
He wasn't able to come to the phone
when I called this morning, J.J.

01:11:24.315 --> 01:11:25.578
He's able to speak.

01:11:25.650 --> 01:11:27.243
He just had a stroke, Dana.

01:11:27.318 --> 01:11:29.013
Where was he,
square-dancing?

01:11:29.087 --> 01:11:30.748
-- What do you want?
-- Excuse me?

01:11:30.822 --> 01:11:32.221
What do you want?

01:11:32.290 --> 01:11:34.759
I want to do my job. I want
to help you, which <i>is</i> my job,

01:11:34.826 --> 01:11:36.692
and I want to do it all
without being treated

01:11:36.761 --> 01:11:38.889
like the guy who just ran over
your dog. How's that?

01:11:38.963 --> 01:11:40.021
That's fine.

01:11:40.098 --> 01:11:41.566
Look, you can't run
the organization

01:11:41.633 --> 01:11:43.067
and run the show
at the same time.

01:11:43.134 --> 01:11:44.624
I don't have to run
the organization.

01:11:44.702 --> 01:11:47.103
He can't talk
on the telephone, Dana.

01:11:54.045 --> 01:11:56.104
Right now, today.

01:11:56.181 --> 01:11:58.912
I'm saying, right now, today, give some
of your responsibilities to Sally.

01:11:58.983 --> 01:12:01.577
-- What's wrong with Natalie? --
We have more confidence in Sally.

01:12:01.653 --> 01:12:03.485
-- I have more confidence in Natalie.
-- Be that as it may.

01:12:03.555 --> 01:12:04.784
<i>You want me to run
the organization</i>

01:12:04.856 --> 01:12:06.517
but let the network
make all the decisions?

01:12:06.591 --> 01:12:09.117
-- I want you and I to work together to
ensure that the network doesn't... -- what?

01:12:09.194 --> 01:12:10.787
Feel the need
to bring in --

01:12:10.862 --> 01:12:11.920
-- <i>An interim managing editor?</i>
-- <i>Yes.</i>

01:12:11.996 --> 01:12:13.088
-- There's no need to do that.
-- I agree.

01:12:13.164 --> 01:12:14.598
That is a bad move.
That is a wrong call.

01:12:14.666 --> 01:12:16.600
And I'll stand in Luther's
office and tell him.

01:12:16.668 --> 01:12:18.432
That's a wrong call.

01:12:18.503 --> 01:12:19.800
Luther could give a damn

01:12:19.871 --> 01:12:21.600
what you think
is a wrong call, Dana.

01:12:21.673 --> 01:12:24.005
He cares what <i>I</i> think
is a wrong call,

01:12:24.075 --> 01:12:25.941
so don't sit there and think
that I need you to like me.

01:12:26.010 --> 01:12:27.603
I'm telling you
the way it is.

01:12:27.679 --> 01:12:29.875
<i>-- He'!-
-- He'!-</i>

01:12:29.948 --> 01:12:31.814
<i>-- He'!-
-- He'!-</i>

