This is weird 'cause this is exactly
where our office used to be.

01:12:35.520 --> 01:12:37.010
We can continue this
in the conference room.

01:12:37.088 --> 01:12:40.456
So, J.J., yesterday
was interesting.

01:12:40.525 --> 01:12:41.515
How so?

01:12:41.593 --> 01:12:43.118
-- How so?
-- Yes.

01:12:43.194 --> 01:12:45.253
Well, McKinney had 41 points
against the Clippers,

01:12:45.330 --> 01:12:47.230
the Diamondbacks won
their fourth in a row...

01:12:47.298 --> 01:12:49.528
And then there was that thing where
somebody tried to blow us up.

01:12:49.601 --> 01:12:51.729
-- <i>Don't</i> take <i>it personally.</i> -- <i>No,
I think I will take it personally.</i>

01:12:51.803 --> 01:12:53.794
The bomb threat was a hoax.

01:12:53.872 --> 01:12:55.738
-- What was it about?
-- Denny Denton.

01:12:55.807 --> 01:12:57.707
-- What <i>about him?</i> -- <i>They
don't iike his radio show.</i>

01:12:57.775 --> 01:12:59.209
I don't like
his radio show, either.

01:12:59.277 --> 01:13:00.711
-- You know what I do?
Change the station. -- What?

01:13:00.778 --> 01:13:02.906
Would that the world were
as enlightened as you, Dan.

01:13:02.981 --> 01:13:04.642
-- Oh, were that it would.
-- Were.

01:13:04.716 --> 01:13:06.309
-- What?
-- Never mind.

01:13:06.384 --> 01:13:08.876
<i>Thank you. When can I see
rough features?</i>

01:13:08.953 --> 01:13:11.388
-- <i>Two hours.</i>
-- <i>Let's go.</i>

01:13:13.958 --> 01:13:15.483
Uh, Dana?

01:13:15.560 --> 01:13:18.086
[Telephone ringing]

01:13:18.162 --> 01:13:20.722
Esther said he's doing
a little better today.

01:13:20.798 --> 01:13:22.766
I'll call in a little bit.

01:13:22.834 --> 01:13:24.563
<i>Dan: You all right?</i>

01:13:24.636 --> 01:13:25.728
Yeah.

01:13:25.803 --> 01:13:26.599
With him?

01:13:26.671 --> 01:13:28.332
[Laughs ] Yeah.

01:13:28.406 --> 01:13:29.669
[Telephone ringing]

01:13:29.741 --> 01:13:32.005
So, we're two
likable guys, right?

01:13:32.076 --> 01:13:34.374
-- I <i>think so.</i> -- <i>I think
we're very likable.</i>

01:13:34.445 --> 01:13:37.244
-- <i>I'm liked</i> wherever I <i>go.</i> -- <i>I'm liked
wherever I go and wherever you go.</i>

01:13:37.315 --> 01:13:38.714
