And yet somebody
tried to blow us up.

01:13:45.690 --> 01:13:47.454
That's what I'm saying.

01:13:47.525 --> 01:13:50.051
-- Does this include Seattle? -- Yes.
It does. -- No. It doesn't.

01:13:50.128 --> 01:13:51.618
-- The film from last night?
-- Yes.

01:13:51.696 --> 01:13:53.221
-- Seattle? It does.
-- Yes. It does.

01:13:53.298 --> 01:13:54.424
-- It doesn't.
-- Dave?

01:13:54.499 --> 01:13:56.399
Hey, Betty, Wilma --
is Seattle on the tape?

01:13:56.467 --> 01:13:57.593
[Knocking on glass]

01:13:57.669 --> 01:13:59.068
Excuse me.

01:13:59.137 --> 01:14:00.229
-- Hey.
-- Hi.

01:14:00.305 --> 01:14:02.273
Good news -- Pluto isn't
being demoted as a planet.

01:14:02.340 --> 01:14:04.365
I need to talk to you.
Can we go in the editing room?

01:14:04.442 --> 01:14:05.432
-- Sure.
-- Thanks.

01:14:05.510 --> 01:14:07.069
Uh, it was gonna be demoted
as a planet.

01:14:07.145 --> 01:14:08.840
It was gonna receive
minor-planet status,

01:14:08.913 --> 01:14:10.972
but apparently there was
an outpouring of protest.

01:14:11.049 --> 01:14:12.778
Doesn't the whole thing
strike you as funny?

01:14:12.850 --> 01:14:15.182
What I'm gonna say might well
seem abrupt and terrible,

01:14:15.253 --> 01:14:17.813
but when I say it, I want you to
remember that the key word --

01:14:17.889 --> 01:14:19.857
the key word --
is "temporarily."

01:14:19.924 --> 01:14:21.949
"Temporarily"
is the key word,

01:14:22.026 --> 01:14:25.826
so there's not gonna be any reason
to be upset or unhappy, okay?

01:14:25.897 --> 01:14:28.730
I think we should
temporarily -- temporarily --

01:14:28.800 --> 01:14:30.268
stop seeing each other.

01:14:32.403 --> 01:14:33.461
Okay.

01:14:33.538 --> 01:14:36.940
-- I'm serious.
-- I know.

01:14:37.008 --> 01:14:39.238
-- I think we should temporarily
stop seeing each other. -- Okay.

01:14:39.310 --> 01:14:40.641
-- I'm serious.
-- I know.

01:14:40.712 --> 01:14:42.441
-- Why are you not unhappy?
-- I don't acknowledge it.

01:14:42.513 --> 01:14:45.244
-- You don't acknowledge it? -- I don't
recognize the breakup. I'm sorry.

01:14:45.316 --> 01:14:47.284
-- No, you can't not recognize it.
