to get my life in order,

01:14:51.823 --> 01:14:53.985
to say nothing of what's
going on with Isaac.

01:14:54.058 --> 01:14:57.119
I mean, this is a good time to
give Dana everything we've got.

01:14:57.195 --> 01:14:59.186
-- I know. -- We need to
stop seeing each other.

01:14:59.263 --> 01:15:00.958
No.

01:15:01.032 --> 01:15:02.898
Wait.

01:15:02.967 --> 01:15:04.696
I break up with you.

01:15:04.769 --> 01:15:06.430
Hmm, not this time.

01:15:06.504 --> 01:15:08.700
