this in order for it to be valid!

01:15:11.142 --> 01:15:13.110
Sweetie, if it makes you feel
better to break up with me,

01:15:13.177 --> 01:15:14.667
that's fine, but I don't
break up with you.

01:15:14.746 --> 01:15:16.009
It doesn't work like that!

01:15:16.080 --> 01:15:17.775
It's working like that
right now.

01:15:17.849 --> 01:15:19.510
-- Does or does not the film
contain Seattle? -- Hang on!

01:15:19.584 --> 01:15:22.053
-- It does. -- It does.
