I'll tell them I can use Sally's
help, but I'm gonna run my show,

01:24:36.206 --> 01:24:38.140
and J.J. can take a seat
in the bleachers.

01:24:38.208 --> 01:24:39.471
Whatever you need.

01:24:39.543 --> 01:24:41.238
I need you,
and I need Isaac back,

01:24:41.312 --> 01:24:44.145
and I need people to stop
trying to blow up the building.

01:24:44.214 --> 01:24:45.613
-- You got me.
-- That's a start.

01:24:45.683 --> 01:24:47.082
Let's go! Two minutes!

01:24:47.151 --> 01:24:49.142
Let's eat 'em up!
Isaac's watching tonight.

01:24:49.219 --> 01:24:52.154
And I think you are absolutely
right about Jeremy, by the way.

01:24:52.222 --> 01:24:53.747
Refusing to accept
the breakup?

01:24:53.824 --> 01:24:55.690
Do not accept it.
It is not recognized.

01:24:55.759 --> 01:24:57.022
It is not valid.

01:24:57.094 --> 01:24:58.357
I agree.

01:24:58.429 --> 01:25:01.330
<i>Roll VTR.
60 seconds live.</i>

01:25:01.398 --> 01:25:03.730
Stand by 2, 2A, 4, and 5.

01:25:03.801 --> 01:25:05.929
<i>-- Loafing FIX-B
-- FIX-S is waded.</i>

01:25:06.003 --> 01:25:07.300
-- No, it's not.
-- It's loaded.

01:25:07.371 --> 01:25:08.861
'Cause I just loaded it now.

01:25:08.939 --> 01:25:10.737
I will kill you both
with my hands.

01:25:10.841 --> 01:25:13.674
-- You're all set. Have a good show.
-- Thank you, Alyson.

01:25:13.711 --> 01:25:14.837
-- Alyson...
-- Yes?

01:25:14.912 --> 01:25:16.607
Don't stand
too close to this wall.

01:25:16.680 --> 01:25:18.648
[Knocking]
It's not real.

01:25:18.716 --> 01:25:20.480
In fact, everybody listen up.

01:25:20.551 --> 01:25:21.916
[Snaps fingers]

01:25:21.986 --> 01:25:24.717
<i>The metallurgy, the structural
wiring, the glass</i> --

01:25:24.788 --> 01:25:28.224
I know we've come to think of this place
as home, but it's a shooting gallery.

01:25:28.292 --> 01:25:32.229
If you hear ticking,
run for your lives.

01:25:32.296 --> 01:25:34.128
Okay, good show.

01:25:34.198 --> 01:25:36.394
<i>Dave: 30 seconds live.</i>

01:25:36.467 --> 01:25:39.164
I'd just like to confirm for everybody
that I am Jeremy's girlfriend.

01:25:39.236 --> 01:25:41.933
-- I am his girlfriend, and he's seen
me naked many times. -- Natalie!

01:25:42.006 --> 01:25:43.474
Sometimes
I do a little dance.

01:25:43.540 --> 01:25:45.975
-- Eyes front, mister!
-- <i>Dave:</i> In 10.

01:25:46.043 --> 01:25:48.410
-- Dan.
-- Yeah?

01:25:48.479 --> 01:25:51.176
I just wanted to say
that if anything terrible

01:25:51.248 --> 01:25:54.047
ever had to happen
to one of us,

01:25:54.118 --> 01:25:55.950
I'd want it to be you.

01:25:56.020 --> 01:25:57.852
Thanks.

01:25:57.921 --> 01:25:59.855
In 3...2...

01:25:59.923 --> 01:26:01.914
Good evening.
From New York City,

01:26:01.992 --> 01:26:04.256
I'm Dan Rydell
alongside Casey McCall.

01:26:04.328 --> 01:26:06.763
Those stories, plus
an Avalanche in Colorado,

01:26:06.830 --> 01:26:08.093
Lightning in Tampa Bay,

01:26:08.165 --> 01:26:09.963
and Warriors
in the Golden State.

01:26:10.034 --> 01:26:11.695
We've got the Suns
moving into Phoenix,

01:26:11.769 --> 01:26:13.931
Hurricanes in Miami,
but guess what.

01:26:14.004 --> 01:26:16.063
Pluto's still a planet.

01:26:16.140 --> 01:26:18.370
All that coming up after this.

01:26:18.442 --> 01:26:22.845
You're watching “Sports Night“
on CSC, so stick around.

